{
  "id": "adv_event_2302_01_02",
  "title": "あなたと\n練習キッス",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます\n……ちょっと早く来過ぎたかな……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning.\n…Did I come a bit too early…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.9,
      "endTime": 6.466666889200001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、ちょうどいいわね）\n（待ってる間、CM撮影の練習をしよう）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But it's just right.）\n（While waiting‚ I should practice for the CM shoot.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.7999998729,
      "endTime": 12.072698084599999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12144.854156099998
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "（渚から借りた恋愛小説もしっかり読み込んだし）\n（感情の流れは問題ない……後は、仕草や演技ね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I've thoroughly studied the romance novel I borrowed from Nagisa-chan）\n（The flow of emotions is fine… now‚ it's about gestures and acting.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.2666665395,
      "endTime": 21.464784558700003,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "……「多くは望まない。だからせめて、口づけを……」\n……ん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"…I don't expect much. So‚ at least‚ a kiss…\"\n…Hmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7333332062,
      "endTime": 28.7441495895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "「言ったでしょ、私に惚れたら火傷するって……」\n……ん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"I told you‚ if you fall for me‚ you'll get burned…\"\n…Hmm…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.1666665395,
      "endTime": 36.009409040499996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "……う～ん……表情とか、こんな感じでいいのかな？\n手を添える場所とか、顔の角度は……うーん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hmm… Is this kind of expression and such okay?\nWhere should I place my hand‚ and what angle for the face… Hmm?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.5333304088,
      "endTime": 47.5901556651,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "（もしかしてキスって、一人だと練習しにくいのかな？）\n（でも、そうよね……普通、二人ですることだし……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Could it be that practicing kissing is difficult alone?）\n（But‚ that's right… normally‚ it's something done by two people…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.033330663,
      "endTime": 57.3516981611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.833330663
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "……あれ？　レッスンルームにいるのは……瑠依？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? Is that Rui in the lesson room?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.633330663,
      "endTime": 63.5867999871,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（それにしても、さっきから何してるんだ？）\n（鏡に向かって……盆踊り？　声掛けてみるか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（By the way‚ what has she been doing for a while now?）\n（Facing the mirror… doing a Bon dance? Should I talk to her?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7867997646,
      "endTime": 73.0981129435,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10795.033995299995
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10795.033995299995
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、瑠依。さっきから何してるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Rui. What have you been up to lately?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.0818337599,
      "endTime": 79.4613575617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、おはようございます\n……そうだ、ちょうど良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ {user}-san.\n…That's right‚ this is perfect timing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.6613573391,
      "endTime": 84.9488573391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "お時間あるようでしたら\n練習相手になってくれませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you have a minute‚\nWould you be my practice partner?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.1613573391,
      "endTime": 88.8680553925,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "練習？　構わないけど、なんの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Practice? I don't mind‚ but practice for what?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.0946906725,
      "endTime": 92.678023974,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "キスです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's for kissing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.8780237514,
      "endTime": 94.0780237514,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、キスの練習……\n――キ、キス！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ kissing practice…\n――K-Kiss!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.711354033,
      "endTime": 99.0289200039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-rui011.m4a",
      "text": "はい。一人だとなんだかうまく出来なくて……\nやっぱり相手がいてくれた方がいいな、と",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ when I try it alone‚ it doesn't seem to work out…\nI just think it would be better if I had someone to practice with.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2326236087,
      "endTime": 107.2679920791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや、でも……！\nだからって、なんで俺が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Well‚ but…!\nWhy me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.4659569421,
      "endTime": 111.1897278957,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-rui012.m4a",
      "text": "だって、今ここにいるの\n{user}さんだけですし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because you're here right now.\nIt's only you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.378133567,
      "endTime": 115.68822999780001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-rui013.m4a",
      "text": "キスの仕方を実演させてもらうだけでいいんです\nそれに私は、演技と割り切れば平気ですから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don't have to do anything except let me practice how to kiss.\nBesides‚ I can handle it if I approach it as acting!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.0447981992,
      "endTime": 122.9862488749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いや、ちょっとはためらってほしいんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd like you to hesitate a bit‚ though…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.1781315325,
      "endTime": 125.9781315325,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 127.3114646433
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "（……え？　え！？　……ど、どういうこと？）\n（今……キスって聞こえたような……ええ！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Huh? What? …What's going on?）\n（Did I just hear… a kiss? Huh!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.3114646433,
      "endTime": 137.73934432649997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.9447979766
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "どないしたん、すみれちゃん\nレッスンルーム、入らへんの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's wrong‚ Sumire-chan?\nCan't you go into the lesson room?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.9447979766,
      "endTime": 142.2615410079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 142.47813131
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "え！？　いや～、その～……\n入りにくいというか、入ってしまうべきというか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!? Well‚ um…\nIt's not that I can't go in‚ it's more like… I should go in…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.47813131,
      "endTime": 150.27632950819998,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10299.999999999984
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.47813131
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "うん？　誰か中におるん？\nゆうても、瑠依ちゃんぐらいしかおらへ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Is someone inside?\nWell‚ there's only Rui-chan inside…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.47813131,
      "endTime": 156.3989645639,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.9447979766
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "……んんん！！？？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hmm!!??",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.6114646433,
      "endTime": 157.9970654963,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2302_01_02-rui014.m4a",
      "text": "一回だけで大丈夫ですから！\nなんならちゃんと契約書交わしますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just once should be fine!\nShould we even exchange a contract for this?",
